snippet.title: Slay the Princess Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
The end of the world is coming sooner than you think...

Art and Animation done by Abby Howard.

Trailer edited by Tony Howard-Arias.

Voice acting by Jonathan Sims and Nichole Goodnight.

Music by Brandon Boone.

Slay the Princess was created by Tony Howard-Arias and Abby Howard.

Get Slay the Princess on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1989270/Slay_the_Princess/
